content:
• January
    • 24 Thurs
      • MBX Maker LAB: CNC & Vacuum Forming Workshop
      • Learn the basics of the MBX Maker LAB CNC and Vacuum Forming Machines. The session will cover the Carvet Desktop CNC, MBX vacuum former, and more.
  • February
    • 7 Thurs
      • 645 @ 6th Street Dive
      • We’re shining a spotlight on brilliant ideas, big passions, and creative projects. At 645, presenters share their stories in just 6 visual minutes.

    • 21 Thurs
      • T-6.6 Pitch Night @ MatchBOX
      • Two pitches and a featured chat. Pizza, beer, and great conversations with Greater Lafayette entrepreneurs, innovators, creatives, and renegades.

    • 23 Sat
      • Free Day at MatchBox
      • Interested in being part of a coworking community for a day? MBX opens the doors to entrepreneurs, innovators, freelancers, designers, hobbyists, developers, and anyone who needs a place to #GetWorkDone on a Friday every month.

    • 24 Sun
      • MBX Maker LAB: 3D Printing Basics Workshop
      • This session is free for MatchBOX members; non-members will receive an email invoice for $15 for the session.

    • 27 Wed
      • MBX Maker LAB: Machines Basics (Beyond 3D Printing and Laser Cutting)
      • This session is free for MatchBOX members; non-members will receive an email invoice for $15 for the session.
  • March
    • 7 Thurs
      • MBXam - March 2018
      • Come as you are and grab a cup of coffee! MBXam is for anyone doing creative work - whether it’s your full-time gig or your side hustle.
  • December
    • 3 Tue
      • Kyle's Birthday
      • Celebrate Kyle's birthday at DelMar Software Development!
